<section class="page-header py-5 text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="fw-bold text-primary">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Protecting your healthcare information is our priority.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5">
  <div class="container">


<div class="card shadow border-0">
  <div class="card-body p-5">

    <h2 class="text-primary mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>

    <p>
      CareConnect collects basic user information such as name,
      email address, appointment details and prescription records
      to provide healthcare management services.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-4">

    <h2 class="text-primary mb-4">How We Use Information</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Appointment Management</li>
      <li>User Authentication</li>
      <li>Prescription Storage</li>
      <li>Improving Platform Performance</li>
      <li>Healthcare Service Optimization</li>
    </ul>

    <hr class="my-4">

    <h2 class="text-primary mb-4">Data Security</h2>

    <p>
      We implement industry-standard security practices to protect
      user information from unauthorized access, disclosure or misuse.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-4">

    <h2 class="text-primary mb-4">Third Party Services</h2>

    <p>
      Certain features may use trusted third-party APIs such as
      healthcare information services. Personal data is not sold
      or shared with third parties.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-4">

    <h2 class="text-primary mb-4">Policy Updates</h2>

    <p>
      CareConnect reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy
      whenever necessary. Continued use of the platform implies
      acceptance of updated policies.
    </p>

  </div>
</div>


  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer py-5 mt-5">
  <div class="container text-center">
